    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p>Cause awareness and giving days are powerful themes upon which to launch online fundraising and social media awareness campaigns. In addition to the days listed below, see also <strong><a href=\"http://publicholidays.global/\">public holidays by country</a></strong>,\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/\">Days of the Year</a></strong>, and\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_commemorative_months\">Wikipedia\u2019s List of Commemorative Months</a></strong>.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2><strong>January</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>17: <a href=\"https://www.pointsoflight.org/mlk-jr-day-of-service/\">Martin Luther King, Jr. Day of Service</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/MLKDay\">#MLKDay</a><br />\n28: <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Data_Privacy_Day\">Data Privacy Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/dataprivacyday\">#DataPrivacyDay</a></strong></p>\n<h2><strong>February</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>2:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.worldwetlandsday.org/\">World Wetlands Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/worldwetlandsday\">#WorldWetlandsDay</a><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_Cancer_Day\"><br />\n</a>4:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.worldcancerday.org/\">World Cancer Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldCancerDay\">#WorldCancerDay</a><br />\n7: <a href=\"https://reclaimsocial.com/\">Reclaim Social</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReclaimSocial\">#ReclaimSocial</a><br />\n</strong><strong>8: <a href=\"https://www.saferinternetday.org/\">Safer Internet Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/saferinternetday\">#SaferInternetDay</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldCancerDay\"><br />\n</a>13:\u00a0<a href=\"https://en.unesco.org/commemorations/worldradioday\">World Radio Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldRadioDay\">#WorldRadioDay</a></strong><strong><br />\n</strong><strong>20:</strong>\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/social-justice-day\">World Day of Social Justice</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/socialjusticeday\">#SocialJusticeDay</a><br />\n22: <a href=\"http://www.digitallearningday.org/\">Digital Learning Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/DigitalLearningDay\">#DigitalLearningDay</a><br />\n22: <a href=\"https://nationaltoday.com/world-spay-day/\">World Spay Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldSpayDay\">#WorldSpayDay</a><br />\n22: <a href=\"https://eventlas.com/world-whale-day/\">World Whale Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldWhaleDay\">#WorldWhaleDay</a><br />\n</strong><strong>27: <a href=\"https://polarbearsinternational.org/get-involved/international-polar-bear-day\">International Polar Bear Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23PolarBearDay&amp;src=typed_query&amp;f=top\">#PolarBearDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23SocialJusticeDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>28: <a href=\"https://www.rarediseaseday.org/\">Rare Disease Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/RareDiseaseDay\">#RareDiseaseDay</a><br />\n</strong></p>\n<h2><strong>March</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>3:\u00a0<a href=\"http://wildlifeday.org/\">World Wildlife Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldWildlifeDay\">#WorldWildlifeDay</a><br />\n8:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.internationalwomensday.com/\">International Women\u2019s Day</a> \u2014 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/IWD2022\">#IWD2022</a></strong><br />\n<strong>10: <a href=\"https://www.worldkidneyday.org/2022-campaign/\">World Kidney\u00a0Day</a> \u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/worldkidneyday\">#WorldKidneyDay</a><br />\n18: <a href=\"https://www.globalrecyclingday.com/\">Global Recycling Day</a> \u2014 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/GlobalRecyclingDay\">#GlobalRecyclingDay</a><br />\n21:\u00a0<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Day_for_the_Elimination_of_Racial_Discrimination\">International Day for the Elimination of Racial Discrimination</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/endracismday\">#EndRacismDay<br />\n</a>21:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.fao.org/international-day-of-forests/en/\">International Day of Forests</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ForestsDay\">#ForestsDay<br />\n</a>21:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.worlddownsyndromeday.org/\">World Down Syndrome Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldDownSyndromeDay\">#WorldDownSyndromeDay</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23ForestsDay\"><br />\n</a>21:\u00a0<a href=\"https://en.unesco.org/commemorations/worldpoetryday\">World Poetry Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldPoetryDay\">#WorldPoetryDay</a><br />\n22:\u00a0<a href=\"http://worldwaterday.org/\">World Water Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldWaterDay\">#WorldWaterDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldWaterDay&amp;src=typd\"><br />\n</a><strong>24:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.stoptb.org/events/world_tb_day/\">World Tuberculosis Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldTBDay\">#WorldTBDay<br />\n</a>26: <a href=\"http://www.earthhour.org/\">Earth Hour</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/EarthHour\">#EarthHour</a><br />\n</strong></p>\n<h2><strong>April</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>2:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.autismspeaks.org/world-autism-awareness-day\">World Autism Awareness Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldAutismDay\">#WorldAustismDay<br />\n</a>3: <a href=\"https://www.good-deeds-day.org/\">Good Deeds Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/gooddeedsday\">#GoodDeedsDay</a><br />\n7:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.who.int/campaigns/world-health-day\">World Health Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldHealthDay\">#WorldHealthDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldAutismDay&amp;src=typd\"><br />\n</a><strong>12: <a href=\"https://www.salveinternational.org/get-involved/april-12th-international-day-for-street-children/\">International Day for Street Children</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/StreetChildrenDay\"><strong>#StreetChildrenDay<br />\n</strong></a><strong>14:</strong>\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/dolphin-day/\">World Dolphin Day</a></strong><strong>\u00a0\u2014</strong>\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldDolphinDay\">#WorldDolphinDay</a><br />\n</strong><strong>15:\u00a0<a href=\"https://en.unesco.org/commemorations/worldartday\">World Art Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldArtDay\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#WorldArtDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23StreetChildrenDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>22:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.earthday.org/\">Earth Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/EarthDay\"><strong>#EarthDay</strong></a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23EarthDay&amp;src=typd\"><strong><br />\n</strong></a><strong>23:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.unesco.org/new/en/wbcd\">World Book Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldBookDay\">#WorldBookDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23EarthDay&amp;src=typd\"><br />\n</a><strong>25: <a href=\"https://www.who.int/campaigns/world-malaria-day\">World Malaria Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldMalariaDay\"><strong>#WorldMalariaDay</strong><br />\n</a><strong>25:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.asoc.org/advocacy/antarctic-wildlife-conservation/penguins/1189\">World Penguin Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldPenguinDay\">#WorldPenguinDay<br />\n</a>30:\u00a0<a href=\"http://jazzday.com/\">International Jazz Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/JazzDay\">#JazzDay</a><br />\n30: <a href=\"https://www.sculpture.org/isday/\">International Sculpture Day</a> \u2014 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/isday\">#ISDay</a><br />\n</strong></p>\n<h2><strong>May</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>3:\u00a0<a href=\"https://en.unesco.org/commemorations/worldpressfreedomday\">World Press Freedom Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldPressFreedomDay\">#WorldPressFreedomDay</a><br />\n8: <a href=\"https://worldovariancancercoalition.org/\">World Ovarian Cancer Day</a>\u00a0\u2014 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WOCD23\">#WOCD23</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?f=realtime&amp;q=%23LabourDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>10: <a href=\"https://www.lupus.org/lupus-awareness-month/world-lupus-day\">World Lupus Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldLupusDay\">#WorldLupusDay</a><br />\n12: <a href=\"https://www.icn.ch/what-we-do/campaigns/international-nurses-day\">International Nurses Day</a>\u00a0\u2014 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/nursesday\">#NursesDay</a><br />\n14: <a href=\"https://fairworldproject.org/choose-fair/world-fair-trade-day/\">World Fair Trade Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldFairTradeDay\">#WorldFairTradeDay</a><br />\n14: <a href=\"https://www.worldmigratorybirdday.org/\">World Migratory Bird Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldMigratoryBirdDay\">#WorldMigratoryBirdDay</a><br />\n</strong><strong>17:\u00a0<a href=\"https://may17.org/\">International Day Against Homophobia, Transphobia, and Biphobia</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/IDAHOBIT\">#IDAHOBIT</a></strong><br />\n<strong>18:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/museum-day/\">International Museum Day</a>\u00a0\u2014 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/MuseumDay\">#MuseumDay</a><br />\n20: <a href=\"http://www.endangered.org/campaigns/endangered-species-day/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Endangered Species Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/EndangeredSpeciesDay\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#EndangeredSpeciesDay</a><br />\n22:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.cbd.int/idb/\">International Day for Biological Diversity</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/BiologicalDiversityDay\">#BiologicalDiversityDay</a></strong><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/WorldTurtleDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>23:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.worldturtleday.org/\">World Turtle Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldTurtleDay\"><strong>#WorldTurtleDay</strong><br />\n</a><strong>31:\u00a0<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_No_Tobacco_Day\">World No Tobacco Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldNoTobaccoDay\">#WorldNoTobaccoDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldTurtleDay&amp;src=typd\"><br />\n</a></p>\n<h2><strong>June</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>5:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/environment-day\">World Environment Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldEnvironmentDay\">#WorldEnvironmentDay</a><br />\n8:\u00a0<a href=\"http://worldoceansday.org/\">World Ocean Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldOceansDay\">#WorldOceanDay<br />\n</a>12:\u00a0<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_Day_Against_Child_Labour\">World Day Against Child Labour</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldDayAgainstChildLabour\">#WorldDayAgainstChildLabour</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldOceansDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>14:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.who.int/campaigns/world-blood-donor-day\">World Blood Donor Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldBloodDonorDay\">#WorldBloodDonorDay</a></strong><br />\n<strong>20:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.unhcr.org/en-us/world-refugee-day.html\">World Refugee Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldRefugeeDay\">#WorldRefugeeDay<br />\n</a>21:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.yogaalliance.org/Events/International_Day_of_Yoga\">International Day of Yoga</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/YogaDay\">#YogaDay<br />\n</a>22:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.worldrainforestday.org/\">World Rainforest Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/worldrainforestday\">#WorldRainforestDay</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23YogaDay\"><br />\n</a>26: <a href=\"https://www.iglta.org/Events/Gay-Pride-Calendar\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Gay Pride Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Pride22\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#Pride22</a></strong></p>\n<hr />\n<p>Our<strong>\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/earn-a-certificate-in-digital-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1653256738392000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1o7aYZXpgFGzJb7CozPKzZ\">Certificate in Digital Marketing &amp; Fundraising</a>\u00a0program covers the fundamentals of website design, email marketing, online fundraising, and social media for nonprofits.</p>\n<p>The program requires the completion of three webinars and costs a total of $100 USD. To earn the certificate, you can attend the webinars live or view the recordings \u2013 or a combination of both.\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/earn-a-certificate-in-digital-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1653256738392000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1o7aYZXpgFGzJb7CozPKzZ\">Learn more &amp; register</a>!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/earn-a-certificate-in-digital-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-37647 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=960%2C755&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"755\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=300%2C236&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=768%2C604&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=50%2C39&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2><strong>July</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>11:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/world-population-day\">WorldPopulationDay</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldPopulationDay\"><strong>#WorldPopulationDay</strong><br />\n</a><strong>18:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.mandeladay.com/\">Nelson Mandela International Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/MandelaDay\">#MandelaDay<br />\n</a>28:</strong>\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/hepatitis/awareness/worldhepday.htm\">World Hepatitis Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldHepatitisDay\">#WorldHepatitisDay</a></strong><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Tiger_Day\"><br />\n</a><strong>29: <a href=\"https://www.wwf.org.uk/get-involved/schools/calendar/international-tiger-day\">International Tiger Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/InternationalTigerDay\">#InternationalTigerDay</a><br />\n30:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.iom.int/world-trafficking-day\">World Day Against Trafficking in Persons</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/EndHumanTrafficking\">#EndHumanTrafficking</a></strong></p>\n<h2><strong>August\u00a0</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>10:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/lion-day/\">World Lion Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldLionDay\" rel=\"noopener\">#WorldLionDay</a><br />\n11: <a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/indigenous-day\">Indigenous People&#8217;s Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/IndigenousDay\"><strong>#IndigenousDay<br />\n</strong></a><strong>12: <a href=\"https://en.unesco.org/commemorations/youthday\">International Youth Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/YouthDay\">#YouthDay</a></strong><a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/indigenousday/\"><br />\n</a><strong>12:\u00a0<a href=\"http://worldelephantday.org/\">World Elephant Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldElephantDay\"><strong>#WorldElephantDay</strong></a><strong><br />\n</strong><strong>17:\u00a0<a href=\"https://nationaldaycalendar.com/days-2/national-nonprofit-day-august-17/\" rel=\"noopener\">National Nonprofit Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/nationalnonprofitday\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#NationalNonprofitDay</a>\u00a0(Internationally recognized)</strong><br />\n<strong>18: <a href=\"https://www.nevergiveupday.com/\">Never Give Up Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/NeverGiveUpDay?src=hashtag_click\">#NeverGiveUpDay</a><br />\n19:\u00a0<a href=\"https://2020.worldhumanitarianday.org/\">World Humanitarian Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldHumanitarianDay\">#WorldHumanitarianDay<br />\n</a></strong><strong>26: <a href=\"https://www.nationaldogday.com/\">National Dog Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/DogDay\">#DogDay</a> (Internationally recognized)<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldHumanitarianDay\"><br />\n</a>29:\u00a0<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Day_against_Nuclear_Tests\">International Day Against Nuclear Tests</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/AgainstNuclearTestsDay\">#AgainstNuclearTestsDay</a></strong></p>\n<h2><strong>September</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>5:\u00a0<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Day_of_Charity\">International Day of Charity</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/CharityDay\">#CharityDay</a><br />\n8:\u00a0<a href=\"https://en.unesco.org/commemorations/literacyday\">International Literacy Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/LiteracyDay\"><strong>#LiteracyDay</strong><br />\n</a><strong>10:\u00a0<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_Suicide_Prevention_Day\">World Suicide Prevention Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldSuicidePreventionDay\"><strong>#WorldSuicidePreventionDay</strong></a><br />\n<strong>15:\u00a0<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Day_of_Democracy\">International Day of Democracy</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/DemocracyDay\">#DemocracyDay</a></strong><a href=\"http://www.internation